<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MASSE — Programme Haut du Corps</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;600;700;800;900&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
--bg: #0a0a0a;
--surface: #111111;
--card: #161616;
--border: #242424;
--red: #e63329;
--red-dim: rgba(230,51,41,0.12);
--red-border: rgba(230,51,41,0.25);
--orange: #f07a2a;
--yellow: #f0c12a;
--text: #e0e0e0;
--muted: #666;
--white: #fff;
}

* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

body {
background: var(--bg);
color: var(--text);
font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
line-height: 1.55;
}

.hero {
padding: 0;
overflow: hidden;
position: relative;
border-bottom: 3px solid var(--red);
}

.hero-inner {
max-width: 960px;
margin: 0 auto;
padding: 56px 28px 48px;
}

.hero-kicker {
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: 13px;
font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 0.22em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--red);
margin-bottom: 14px;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 10px;
}

.hero-kicker::before {
content: '';
display: inline-block;
width: 28px;
height: 2px;
background: var(--red);
}

.hero h1 {
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 8.5rem);
font-weight: 900;
line-height: 0.88;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--white);
letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}

.hero h1 span {
color: var(--red);
display: block;
}

.hero-stats {
display: flex;
flex-wrap: wrap;
gap: 0;
margin-top: 32px;
border: 1px solid var(--border);
border-radius: 4px;
overflow: hidden;
max-width: 620px;
}

.hstat {
flex: 1;
min-width: 120px;
padding: 14px 18px;
border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.hstat:last-child { border-right: none; }

.hstat-val {
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: 1.8rem;
font-weight: 800;
color: var(--red);
line-height: 1;
}

.hstat-label {
font-size: 10px;
font-weight: 600;
letter-spacing: 0.1em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--muted);
margin-top: 3px;
}

.wrap {
max-width: 960px;
margin: 0 auto;
padding: 0 28px;
}

.sec-head {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 12px;
padding: 40px 0 20px;
}

.sec-head h2 {
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 800;
letter-spacing: 0.2em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--red);
}

.sec-head::after {
content: '';
flex: 1;
height: 1px;
background: var(--border);
}

.week-grid {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);
gap: 4px;
margin-bottom: 44px;
}

.wday {
background: var(--card);
border: 1px solid var(--border);
padding: 12px 6px;
text-align: center;
border-radius: 3px;
}

.wday.active-day { border-color: var(--red); }
.wday.rest-day { opacity: 0.4; }

.wday-name {
font-size: 9px;
font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 0.14em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--muted);
margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.wday-focus {
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: 13px;
font-weight: 700;
text-transform: uppercase;
line-height: 1.2;
}

.wday-focus.c-red { color: var(--red); }
.wday-focus.c-orange { color: var(--orange); }
.wday-focus.c-yellow { color: var(--yellow); }
.wday-focus.c-muted { color: var(--muted); font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; }

.tabs {
display: flex;
gap: 2px;
margin-bottom: 20px;
overflow-x: auto;
scrollbar-width: none;
-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
}

.tabs::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

.tab-btn {
flex-shrink: 0;
padding: 12px 20px;
background: var(--surface);
border: 1px solid var(--border);
border-radius: 2px;
color: var(--muted);
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: 14px;
font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 0.08em;
text-transform: uppercase;
cursor: pointer;
transition: all 0.15s;
white-space: nowrap;
min-height: 44px;
touch-action: manipulation;
-webkit-user-select: none;
user-select: none;
}

.tab-btn:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: #444; }

.tab-btn.active {
background: var(--red);
border-color: var(--red);
color: #fff;
}

.tab-btn.rest-tab.active {
background: var(--surface);
border-color: var(--border);
color: var(--muted);
}

.tab-content { display: none; }
.tab-content.active { display: block; }

.day-card {
background: var(--card);
border: 1px solid var(--border);
border-radius: 4px;
overflow: hidden;
}

.day-hdr {
padding: 22px 24px 18px;
border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
background: var(--surface);
display: flex;
justify-content: space-between;
align-items: flex-start;
flex-wrap: wrap;
gap: 12px;
}

.day-hdr-left .day-num {
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 0.2em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--red);
}

.day-hdr-left .day-name {
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: 2rem;
font-weight: 900;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--white);
line-height: 1;
margin-top: 2px;
}

.badges {
display: flex;
gap: 6px;
flex-wrap: wrap;
align-items: flex-start;
}

.badge {
padding: 4px 10px;
border-radius: 2px;
font-size: 10px;
font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 0.08em;
text-transform: uppercase;
}

.badge-red { background: var(--red-dim); color: var(--red); border: 1px solid var(--red-border); }
.badge-orange { background: rgba(240,122,42,0.12); color: var(--orange); border: 1px solid rgba(240,122,42,0.25); }
.badge-yellow { background: rgba(240,193,42,0.12); color: var(--yellow); border: 1px solid rgba(240,193,42,0.25); }
.badge-gray { background: rgba(102,102,102,0.12); color: var(--muted); border: 1px solid rgba(102,102,102,0.2); }

.warmup {
padding: 13px 24px;
border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
font-size: 13px;
color: var(--muted);
background: rgba(230,51,41,0.04);
}

.warmup strong { color: var(--red); }

.ex-table {
width: 100%;
border-collapse: collapse;
}

.ex-table thead tr {
background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

.ex-table th {
padding: 9px 16px;
text-align: left;
font-size: 9px;
font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 0.15em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--muted);
border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.ex-table td {
padding: 14px 16px;
border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(36,36,36,0.7);
vertical-align: middle;
font-size: 14px;
}

.ex-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.ex-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); }

.ex-name {
font-weight: 600;
color: var(--white);
display: block;
font-size: 14px;
}

.ex-tip {
font-size: 11px;
color: var(--muted);
margin-top: 3px;
display: block;
line-height: 1.5;
}

.muscle-tag {
display: inline-block;
padding: 3px 8px;
border-radius: 2px;
font-size: 10px;
font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 0.06em;
text-transform: uppercase;
white-space: nowrap;
}

.m-chest { background: rgba(230,51,41,0.15); color: var(--red); }
.m-back { background: rgba(240,122,42,0.15); color: var(--orange); }
.m-shoulders { background: rgba(240,193,42,0.15); color: var(--yellow); }
.m-biceps { background: rgba(110,200,240,0.15); color: #6ec8f0; }
.m-triceps { background: rgba(200,240,110,0.12); color: #c8f06e; }
.m-traps { background: rgba(180,110,240,0.15); color: #c87ef0; }
.m-core { background: rgba(102,102,102,0.15); color: var(--muted); }

.sr {
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: 18px;
font-weight: 800;
color: var(--white);
white-space: nowrap;
letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}

.rest-t {
font-size: 11px;
color: var(--muted);
}

.cooldown {
padding: 13px 24px;
border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
font-size: 13px;
color: var(--muted);
background: rgba(240,122,42,0.04);
}

.cooldown strong { color: var(--orange); }

.rest-card {
background: var(--card);
border: 1px solid var(--border);
border-radius: 4px;
padding: 48px 32px;
text-align: center;
}

.rest-card .ri { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }

.rest-card h3 {
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: 1.8rem;
font-weight: 900;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--muted);
margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.rest-card p {
font-size: 14px;
color: var(--muted);
max-width: 380px;
margin: 0 auto;
}

.macro-row {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
gap: 8px;
margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.macro-box {
background: var(--card);
border: 1px solid var(--border);
border-radius: 3px;
padding: 18px 20px;
}

.macro-box-label {
font-size: 9px;
font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 0.18em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--muted);
margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.macro-box-val {
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: 2.4rem;
font-weight: 900;
line-height: 1;
}

.macro-box-note {
font-size: 11px;
color: var(--muted);
margin-top: 5px;
line-height: 1.5;
}

.meals {
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
gap: 6px;
margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.meal {
background: var(--card);
border: 1px solid var(--border);
border-radius: 3px;
padding: 15px 20px;
display: flex;
gap: 20px;
align-items: flex-start;
}

.meal-t {
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: 13px;
font-weight: 800;
letter-spacing: 0.1em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--red);
min-width: 80px;
padding-top: 1px;
}

.meal-body strong {
display: block;
font-size: 13px;
font-weight: 600;
color: var(--white);
margin-bottom: 2px;
}

.meal-body span {
font-size: 12px;
color: var(--muted);
line-height: 1.6;
}

.keys-grid {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
gap: 8px;
margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.key-card {
background: var(--card);
border: 1px solid var(--border);
border-radius: 3px;
padding: 18px;
display: flex;
gap: 14px;
align-items: flex-start;
}

.key-icon {
font-size: 1.3rem;
flex-shrink: 0;
margin-top: 1px;
}

.key-card strong {
display: block;
font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
font-size: 15px;
font-weight: 800;
text-transform: uppercase;
letter-spacing: 0.04em;
color: var(--white);
margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.key-card p {
font-size: 12px;
color: var(--muted);
line-height: 1.6;
}

.important-box {
background: var(--red-dim);
border: 1px solid var(--red-border);
border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
border-radius: 3px;
padding: 16px 20px;
margin-bottom: 20px;
font-size: 13px;
color: var(--text);
line-height: 1.6;
}

.important-box strong { color: var(--red); }

.divider { height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin-bottom: 0; }

.footer {
text-align: center;
padding: 32px 28px 48px;
font-size: 11px;
color: #333;
letter-spacing: 0.08em;
text-transform: uppercase;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
.week-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
.ex-table th:nth-child(4), .ex-table td:nth-child(4) { display: none; }
.day-hdr { flex-direction: column; }
.hero h1 { font-size: 3.8rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
<div class="hero-inner">
<div class="hero-kicker">Programme prise de masse · Haut du corps</div>
<h1>Build<br><span>du muscle.</span></h1>
<div class="hero-stats">
<div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-val">63<span style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--muted)"> kg</span></div><div class="hstat-label">Poids actuel</div></div>
<div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-val">1m80</div><div class="hstat-label">Taille</div></div>
<div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-val">5</div><div class="hstat-label">Jours / semaine</div></div>
<div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-val">3000<span style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--muted)"> kcal</span></div><div class="hstat-label">Cible calorique</div></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
<div class="sec-head"><h2>Semaine type</h2></div>
<div class="week-grid">
<div class="wday active-day"><div class="wday-name">Lun</div><div class="wday-focus c-red">Poitrine<br>Triceps</div></div>
<div class="wday active-day"><div class="wday-name">Mar</div><div class="wday-focus c-orange">Dos<br>Biceps</div></div>
<div class="wday rest-day"><div class="wday-name">Mer</div><div class="wday-focus c-muted">Repos</div></div>
<div class="wday active-day"><div class="wday-name">Jeu</div><div class="wday-focus c-yellow">Épaules<br>Trapèzes</div></div>
<div class="wday active-day"><div class="wday-name">Ven</div><div class="wday-focus c-red">Bras<br>Focus</div></div>
<div class="wday active-day"><div class="wday-name">Sam</div><div class="wday-focus c-orange">Full<br>Upper</div></div>
<div class="wday rest-day"><div class="wday-name">Dim</div><div class="wday-focus c-muted">Repos</div></div>
</div>

<div class="important-box">
<strong>Important pour toi :</strong> À 63 kg pour 1m80, tu es en morphologie ectomorphe — métabolisme rapide, difficile de prendre du poids. Les règles sont différentes : <strong>moins de cardio</strong> (brûle trop de calories), <strong>repos obligatoire</strong> (le muscle pousse pendant la récup), et <strong>manger BEAUCOUP</strong> est aussi important que s'entraîner. Sans surplus calorique, le programme ne servira à rien.
</div>

<div class="sec-head"><h2>Programme détaillé</h2></div>

<div class="tabs" id="tabNav">
<button class="tab-btn active" data-day="lundi">Lundi — Poitrine</button>
<button class="tab-btn" data-day="mardi">Mardi — Dos</button>
<button class="tab-btn rest-tab" data-day="mercredi">Mer 😴</button>
<button class="tab-btn" data-day="jeudi">Jeudi — Épaules</button>
<button class="tab-btn" data-day="vendredi">Vendredi — Bras</button>
<button class="tab-btn" data-day="samedi">Samedi — Full</button>
<button class="tab-btn rest-tab" data-day="dimanche">Dim 😴</button>
</div>

<!-- LUNDI -->
<div id="tab-lundi" class="tab-content active">
<div class="day-card">
<div class="day-hdr">
<div class="day-hdr-left"><div class="day-num">Lundi · Séance 1</div><div class="day-name">Poitrine + Triceps</div></div>
<div class="badges"><span class="badge badge-red">~55 min</span><span class="badge badge-orange">Pectoraux focus</span><span class="badge badge-gray">Barre + Haltères</span></div>
</div>
<div class="warmup"><strong>🔥 Échauffement (8 min) :</strong> 5 min vélo léger + 2 séries pompes légères 15 reps + rotations épaules + bras croisés 10 reps</div>
<table class="ex-table">
<thead><tr><th>Exercice</th><th>Muscles</th><th>Séries × Reps</th><th>Repos</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td><span class="ex-name">Développé couché barre 🏆</span><span class="ex-tip">L'exercice roi. Descendre la barre jusqu'à effleurer la poitrine, pousser en explosant. Progression de charge chaque semaine.</span></td><td><span class="muscle-tag m-chest">Pectoraux</span></td><td class="sr">5 × 6–8</td><td class="rest-t">2–3 min</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="ex-name">Développé incliné haltères</span><span class="ex-tip">Banc à 30–45°, travaille le haut des pecs. Contrôle la descente en 2 secondes.</span></td><td><span class="muscle-tag m-chest">Pectoraux haut</span></td><td class="sr">4 × 8–10</td><td class="rest-t">90 s</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="ex-name">Écarté haltères sur banc plat</span><span class="ex-tip">Grand arc de cercle, coudes légèrement fléchis — étirement max en bas, squeeze en haut.</span></td><td><span class="muscle-tag m-chest">Pectoraux</span></td><td class="sr">3 × 12</td><td class="rest-t">75 s</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="ex-name">Dips prise large (lest si possible)</span><span class="ex-tip">Prise large + buste penché en avant = pectoraux. Si trop facile : mettre un haltère entre les pieds.</span></td><td><span class="muscle-tag m-chest">Pecs + Triceps</span></td><td class="sr">4 × 10–12</td><td class="rest-t">90 s</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="ex-name">Extension triceps poulie haute</span><span class="ex-tip">Coudes fixes contre le corps, descendre jusqu'à l'extension complète — triceps long.</span></td><td><span class="muscle-tag m-triceps">Triceps</span></td><td class="sr">4 × 12–15</td><td class="rest-t">60 s</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="ex-name">Développé couché prise serrée</span><span class="ex-tip">Mains rapprochées (30 cm d'écart), mêmes mouvements que le DC normal — triceps en feu.</span></td><td><span class="muscle-tag m-triceps">Triceps</span></td><td class="sr">3 × 10</td><td class="rest-t">75 s</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<div class="cooldown"><strong>🧊 Cooldown (5 min) :</strong> Étirement pectoraux (bras en croix contre un mur), étirement triceps derrière la tête, rotations cervicales</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- MARDI -->
<div id="tab-mardi" class="tab-content">
<div class="day-card">
<div class="day-hdr">
<div class="day-hdr-left"><div class="day-num">Mardi · Séance 2</div><div class="day-name">Dos + Biceps</div></div>
<div class="badges"><span class="badge badge-red">~55 min</span><span class="badge badge-orange">Largeur du dos</span><span class="badge badge-gray">Barre + Poulie</span></div>
</div>
<div class="warmup"><strong>🔥 Échauffement (8 min) :</strong> Rotations d'épaules, face pulls légers, 2 séries de tractions (ou tirage) à vide + étirement latissimus</div>
<table class="ex-table">
<thead><tr><th>Exercice</th><th>Muscles</th><th>Séries × Reps</th><th>Repos</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td><span class="ex-name">Tractions prise large 🏆</span><span class="ex-tip">L'exercice qui donne le V du dos. Mouvement complet : bras tendus en bas, menton au-dessus de la barre. Si trop dur : tirage poulie haute prise large.</span></td><td><span class="muscle-tag m-back">Dos (latissimus)</span></td><td class="sr">5 × max</td><td class="rest-t">2–3 min</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="ex-name">Rowing barre buste penché</span><span class="ex-tip">Dos à 45°, tirer vers le bas-ventre, coudes le long du corps — épaisseur du dos.</span></td><td><span class="muscle-tag m-back">Dos moyen</span></td><td class="sr">4 × 8–10</td><td class="rest-t">2 min</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="ex-name">Tirage poulie basse (machine dos)</span><span class="ex-tip">Assis, tirer vers le ventre, sortir la poitrine, squeeze en fin de mouvement — garder le dos droit.</span></td><td><span class="muscle-tag m-back">Dos + Biceps</span></td><td class="sr">4 × 10–12</td><td class="rest-t">90 s</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="ex-name">Rowing haltère 1 bras (sur banc)</span><span class="ex-tip">1 genou sur le banc, tirer haut vers la hanche, coude au plafond — pleine amplitude.</span></td><td><span class="muscle-tag m-back">Grand dorsal</span></td><td class="sr">3 × 12/côté</td><td class="rest-t">75 s</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="ex-name">Curl barre EZ (biceps)</span><span class="ex-tip">Coudes fixes, pas de balancement — montée explosive, descente contrôlée 2 secondes.</span></td><td><span class="muscle-tag m-biceps">Biceps</span></td><td class="sr">4 × 10</td><td class="rest-t">75 s</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="ex-name">Curl haltères marteau</span><span class="ex-tip">Prise neutre (pouces vers le haut) — travaille le brachial et l'avant-bras. Épaisseur du bras.</span></td><td><span class="muscle-tag m-biceps">Biceps + Brachial</span></td><td class="sr">3 × 12</td><td class="rest-t">60 s</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<div class="cooldown"><strong>🧊 Cooldown (5 min) :</strong> Étirement grand dorsal (accroché à une barre), étirement biceps bras tendu contre mur, décompression lombaire enfant</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- MERCREDI REPOS -->
<div id="tab-mercredi" class="tab-content">
<div class="rest-card">
<div class="ri">😴</div>
<h3>Mercredi — Repos</h3>
<p>Le muscle ne pousse pas en salle, il pousse pendant le repos. Journée off totale ou marche légère max 30 min. Mange bien quand même — le corps reconstruit toujours.</p>
</div>
</div>

<!-- JEUDI -->
<div id="tab-jeudi" class="tab-content">
<div class="day-card">
<div class="day-hdr">
